#IAM Policies to work with Functions

Allow service FaaS to read repos in tenancy
Allow service FaaS to use virtual-network-family in compartment <comp-name>

#If one or more Oracle Functions users is not tenancy administrator, add the following policy statements to the new policy:

Allow group <group-name> to manage repos in tenancy
Allow group <group-name> to use virtual-network-family in compartment <comp-name>
Allow group <group-name> to manage functions-family in compartment <compartment-name>
Allow group <group-name< to read metrics in compartment <compartment-name>